# papers /.guide — cold-entry navigation (raw 0 root-ssot 동반)
# Created 2026-04-28

== papers 프로젝트 개요 ==
- 논문/DOI archive (Zenodo + OSF dual-publish)
- manifest.json: 433+ paper entries (canonical SSOT)
- bin/papers: unified 12-verb CLI

== 진입점 ==
1. `papers help` — 모든 subcommand
2. `papers list --status published` — manifest 쿼리
3. `papers scan meta --selftest` — meta scanner 자가검사
4. `papers lint` — .own 8 rules 검사

== SSOT 파일 ==
- .own       — 8 governance rules
- .roadmap   — phase checkpoint
- .raw-ref   — hexa-lang /.raw mirror pin
- manifest.json — paper entries
- README.md  — public-facing

== 도구 디렉토리 ==
- bin/papers       — bash dispatcher (12 verbs)
- tool/*.hexa      — 11 hexa tools
- tool/lib/        — shared helpers
- docs/            — design notes
- state/           — audit ledgers + scan output

== 주요 워크플로 ==
- 신규 paper 추가:    papers pull <doi>  (Phase 2)
- DOI 정합 검증:      papers verify <id>
- Zenodo 발행:        papers publish <id>
- OSF dual-publish:   papers publish <id> --target=all
- manifest sync:      papers sync
- raw 명명/스키마 lint: papers lint

== secret CLI 통합 ==
papers는 `secret get zenodo.token`, `secret get osf.token` 으로 credential 추출.
직접 토큰 입력 금지 (own#3 papers-secret-only-token-source).

등록: `secret set zenodo.token` (사용자 직접)
